{"tid":2122670,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"長袖衫遮手帶 9內地漢元朗徘徊 稱正赴東涌檢疫 警載巴士站轉車","createTime":"2020-07-24T06:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T10:42:13.000Z","uid":279819,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"76459f16c030ead3299fc196a9f241716007cbbb","tid":2122670,"uid":279819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:33:52.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】元朗昨日有9名從內地來港的拖篋男子在街頭徘徊，各人均穿上長袖上衣，手腕上的強制檢疫手帶被遮蓋。有途人見狀報警，警方到場了解後，眾人稱正前往檢疫。警員徵詢衛生署意見後，以警車將9人送往附近巴士站，讓他們自行前往檢疫。有區議員批評有關安排不合理。<br />\n<br />\n警方稱昨午1時12分接獲報案，指9人報稱剛從深圳灣口岸入境，正經元朗轉車往東涌石門甲隔離，警員其後以警車接載眾人到附近巴士站轉車，案件列作投訴。本報昨向衛生署查詢，截稿前未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n未超衛署2小時規定 區議員轟安排存漏洞<br />\n元朗區議員石景澄表示，昨下午1時許接獲街坊報料，石趕往現場發現約8至9人，全部人均穿著長袖上衣遮蓋強制檢疫手帶。他向在場警員了解，得悉各人剛從深圳灣口岸入境，正前往入境時申報的處所隔離途中，並未超出衛生署規定的兩小時時限。石引述警員稱，徵詢衛生署意見後，下午3時許按署方指示以警車送他們就近巴士站，讓他們自行前往隔離。<br />\n<br />\n石景澄表示，入境後強制檢疫者兩小時內自行乘公共交通工具前往檢疫，途中會和多人接觸，有可能感染他人，指安排有漏洞。石稱，以昨日事件為例，眾人身穿長袖衫，認為他們故意遮蓋手帶，而在元朗徘徊亦不知道他們是否真的在等車或打算前往購物，警員截獲後應立即將他們送往檢疫，而非由他們自行前往，會向衛生署舉報事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://translate.google.com/#view=home&amp;op=translate&amp;sl=zh-CN&amp;tl=en&amp;text=%E5%80%8B%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E4%BF%82%E5%9B%9E%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%94%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%8A%E9%A3%9B%E6%A9%9F%E9%99%A4%E9%9D%9E%E5%9C%B0%E7%91%BE%E7%9D%87%E5%94%94%E9%9C%80%E7%9D%87%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E7%9A%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftranslate.google.com%2F%23view%3Dhome%26op%3Dtranslate%26sl%3Dzh-CN%26tl%3Den%26text%3D%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%259B%259E%25E7%25A8%258B%25E8%25BF%2594%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25B8%258A%25E9%25A3%259B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E9%2599%25A4%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2591%25BE%25E7%259D%2587%25E5%2594%2594%25E9%259C%2580%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%259B%25AE%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%258F%2597%25E7%259A%2584&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6KpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=09e36a88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://translate.google.com/#view=home&amp;op=translate&amp;sl=zh-CN&amp;tl=en&amp;text=%E5%80%8B%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E4%BF%82%E5%9B%9E%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%94%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%8A%E9%A3%9B%E6%A9%9F%E9%99%A4%E9%9D%9E%E5%9C%B0%E7%91%BE%E7%9D%87%E5%94%94%E9%9C%80%E7%9D%87%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E7%9A%84</a>"},{"pid":"e7e344d4dcfd80153bbf031fd2b0c3d608d6292d","tid":2122670,"uid":279819,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:38:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eHfnHfR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeHfnHfR.jpg&h=ca94284d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb351167126632e878dd2636dabde0c80e4321be","tid":2122670,"uid":253954,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:40:56.000Z","msg":"大家出街見到D夏日炎炎仲著長袖衫既人要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc02f030d89835e41e442c20c306ccad61988f1","tid":2122670,"uid":24788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:47:09.000Z","msg":"來疫區香港做咩<br />\n好奇怪"},{"pid":"680286fbdf1b89f5f21c40a28b15bd42814b4937","tid":2122670,"uid":49643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:49:02.000Z","msg":"政府真係癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69829812e5fc518e07f523f1ac392cc53f21b8cd","tid":2122670,"uid":96486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:49:51.000Z","msg":"果然係一等公民"},{"pid":"2562b6cd885c30d3632ebad0607fa64554ad791d","tid":2122670,"uid":243677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:59:13.000Z","msg":"公安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ddc3c9904a0a1459e4142ef30eddb79269ec715","tid":2122670,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:06:04.000Z","msg":"生化武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b135fdb86f52bacfe9635